  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Asacol™ 4.8 g/day (800 mg tablets) is statistically significant more effective to induce
      clinical and endoscopic remission after 6 weeks of treatment compared to placebo in subjects
      with active ulcerative colitis (UC).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
